	* gtk/src/icontheme.hg: added refreturns for get_default and get_for_screen.
	* gtk/src/settings.hg: added unwrapped properties.
	* gtk/src/targetlist.[hg|ccg]: added a create method that wraps
	gtk_target_list_new.

